    Q3{<b>Needs external<br/>documents?</b><br/><span style='font-size:11px;color:#6d28d9'>private / fresh / precise</span>}:::decision
    Q4{<b>Multiple tools or<br/>dynamic steps?</b>}:::decision

    T1[<b>Direct Call</b><br/><span style='font-size:11px;color:#6d28d9'>single prompt → response</span>]:::tier1
    T2[<b>Chained Calls</b><br/><span style='font-size:11px;color:#6d28d9'>pipeline of LLM steps</span>]:::tier2
    T3[<b>RAG</b><br/><span style='font-size:11px;color:#6d28d9'>Retrieval-Augmented Generation</span>]:::tier3
    T4[<b>Agent</b><br/><span style='font-size:11px;color:#6d28d9'>autonomous tool selection</span>]:::tier4
    T5[<b>Reconsider the task</b><br/><span style='font-size:11px;color:#6d28d9'>scope may be unclear</span>]:::neutral

    START --> Q1
